{
  "stem": "20405.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyway, this kapo in Birkenau after we said we were barber with Dario, they took us to a big room over there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My god.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When opened the doors, what we saw over there sardines just with their head down, all women dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how were in there, 500, 600, 1,000.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So the kapo took us, took one of the scissor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They gave us two big scissors like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They want to use it for the-- for lambs, to cut the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] for the sheeps, they cut the--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The wool.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They cut the wool from--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the wool, to cut the wool so big.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he took one of the scissor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went on top of those dead bodies, get into a women's hair like that, and cut it, and through their hair's down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] cut them [INAUDIBLE], threw them down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is the way you're going to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got so scared, we, Dario.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because even when we were young, talking about dead people or about cemeteries, we were scared at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because were some scaries of-- the scary stories, they were-- and we were scare about dead bodies, dead people, so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we saw that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Are the-- are the people dead over here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, but we were scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the kapo had a stick on his hand and were beating us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went on top of the-- when we were over there, we start-- he got again the scissor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, faster, faster.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was going, jumping from one body to another, to another, [INAUDIBLE] this kapo.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bah, bah, bah, bah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With Dario, we could not do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
